unittitle_ssm: Records of the Andiron Club of New York City
abstract_ssm: The collection documents the operation of the Andiron Club of New York City since its founding in 1907. It includes correspondence with members and visiting speakers; minutes of Council and general meetings; curricula vitae and lists of the membership; financial records; photographs; publications; and reprints.
